                Mr. Foot
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-38362481-b03e-4eaf-9646-34fdb34b5eeb" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1938-02-01/debates/aa4feec8-7f0d-47d4-8ebc-39fbdc939ea5/MoneyBills(Procedure)#contribution-38362481-b03e-4eaf-9646-34fdb34b5eeb">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
