<p class="">I do not understand that to be the position. I understand that he was giving evidence to the Committee as an expert on Parliamentary procedure and not in this case in his capacity as secretary to the Parliamentary Labour party.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-1482fa28-852a-4c72-82a9-059e521fa301" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
